text: John Freind may refer to: *Sir John Freind (conspirator) or John Friend (died 1696), English civil servant; executed *John Freind (physician) (1675–1728), English physician *Sir John Freind Robinson, 1st Baronet (1754–1832) English Archdeacon of Armagh ==See also== *John Friend (disambiguation)
